1) create spring boot project
2)build jar using mvn package
3)install docker desktop
4)go to build -> active build -> copy given command "docker buildx build ."
5)run this cmd in terminal in intellij
6)it will build image that we can see in docker desktop.
7)check by running container and image
8)to access endpoint we need to run "docker run -p 8080:8080 <imageName>"
9)check to access endpoint

#imp commands

#tag image in lowercase
docker tag dockerapp.jar:latest kjansari/dockerapp
#push image to dockerhub
docker push <DockerUsername>/<imageName>


#generated render URL sample

https://dockerapp-v91o.onrender.com/hello

